dcterms:description: The OpenfMRI dataset includes 221 subjects (122 healthy controls, 50 schizophrenia subjects, and 49 bipolar disorder patients) with T1w anatomical MPRAGE images and resting-state fMRI data.
dcterms:title: OpenfMRI dataset

dcterms:description: The private BD dataset was collected from the Psychiatric Hospital of Zhumadian from 2014 to 2018, consisting of 91 subjects (52 bipolar disorder patients and 39 healthy controls) with T1w anatomical MPRAGE and resting-state fMRI data.
dcterms:title: BD dataset
